  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    UK statement to the WTO General Council
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The UK's Ambassador to the WTO in Geneva, Julian Braithwaite, delivered this statement at the WTO General Council under Item 8: Procedural Guidelines for WTO Councils and Committees Addressing Trade Concerns – Statement by Co-Sponsors of WT/GC/W/777/Rev.5</p>

  </div>
</div>

